<h3 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage">#</a> Usage</h3>
<p><strong>CdrGrid</strong> functions as a grid container, and it's immediate children are grid items.</p>
<ul>
<li>Use any native CSS grid properties on the CdrGrid or it's grid items</li>
<li>Use media queries to add responsiveness to your grid layout</li>
<li>Wrap your entire page layout in a single <code>cdr-container</code></li>
</ul>
